IMAPAccount miikanissi
Host imap.mailfence.com
Port 993
User miikanissi
PassCmd "pass email/mailfence/miika.nissi@mailfence.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore miikanissi-remote
Account miikanissi

MaildirStore miikanissi-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/miikanissi/
Inbox ~/Mail/miikanissi/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/miikanissi/Trash

Channel miikanissi
Far :miikanissi-remote:
Near :miikanissi-local:
Patterns INBOX "Sent Items" Drafts Trash Spam?
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
MaxMessages 0